@highlight

The purpose of the study ( observational and prospective ) is to evaluate the efficacy and tolerability of the methadone maintenance treatment in patients addicted to heroin.

 The efficacy and tolerability are assessed by correlating to the adequacy of the dosage of methadone.

 The patients will be observed for two years.

